Usage: readSdpFile [-help] -file <sdpFileName> [-leftoverGroup]
                   [-origin <llx> <lly>] [-skipPlacement] [-hierPath <path> ]

-help                   # Prints out the command usage
-file <sdpFileName>     # Sdp file name. (string, required)
-hierPath <path>        # hierarcial path name. (string, optional)
-leftoverGroup          # store remaining instances to a group (bool, optional)
-origin <llx> <lly>     # sdp block origin (point, optional)
-skipPlacement          # don't place the sdp group, only read in the group
                        # definition (bool, optional)